    Note that we also want to deprecate and remove
    */googAutoGainControl/* and */googNoiseSuppression/*.
    The counters for these two have higher values because they also
    include the counts for the corresponding standard constraints
    */autoGainControl/* and /noiseSupression/ as they are considered
    the same at the point where they are being counted.

    googAutoGainControl
    &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://www.chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/1949"&gt;https://www.chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/1949&lt;/a&gt;
