    They have similar values to (the also standard)
    */echoCancellation/* 
(&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/1930"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/1930&lt;/a&gt;),
    so we are confident that those counters are expressing standard
    usage, so the goog-prefixed variant can be removed.



