&gt;&gt;&gt; ::before::marker and ::after::marker pseudo elements and will be essential 
&gt;&gt;&gt; to style ::column::scroll-marker pseudo elements for the carousel project (
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/flackr/carousel/tree/main/fragmentation"&gt;https://github.com/flackr/carousel/tree/main/fragmentation&lt;/a&gt;).
