&gt;&gt;&gt; Summary 
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Allows to style pseudo elements that are nested inside other pseudo 
&gt;&gt;&gt; elements. So far, support is defined for: ::before::marker ::after::marker 
