&gt; 1053)
&gt;
&gt; *WebKit*: Support (&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/&lt;/a&gt;
&gt; standards-positions/issues/375)
&gt;
&gt; *Web developers*: Positive (&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/whatwg/dom/issues/1255"&gt;https://github.com/whatwg/dom/issues/1255&lt;/a&gt;) 
&gt; See comments from *HTMX* 
&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://x.com/htmx_org/status/1790414137765294340"&gt;https://x.com/htmx_org/status/1790414137765294340&lt;/a&gt;&gt; (docs 
&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://htmx.org/examples/move-before/"&gt;https://htmx.org/examples/move-before/&lt;/a&gt;&gt;) &amp; *React* 
&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://gist.github.com/gaearon/ad9347f1f809b6fe5af15bb911bbaf6b#moving-and-reparenting-without-losing-state"&gt;https://gist.github.com/gaearon/ad9347f1f809b6fe5af15bb911bbaf6b#moving-and-reparenting-without-losing-state&lt;/a&gt;&gt;,
&gt;  
&gt; as well as *Angular* 
&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/whatwg/dom/issues/1255#issuecomment-2044930653"&gt;https://github.com/whatwg/dom/issues/1255#issuecomment-2044930653&lt;/a&gt;&gt;.
