&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *WebKit*: No signal
&gt;&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Would this take us further away from WebKit interop? What's the current
&gt; state of their implementation?
&gt;

getCoalescedPoints and getPredictedPoints aren't implemented by WebKit at
all


