&lt;pre&gt;On Wed, Nov 13, 2024 at 10:38 AM Rune Lillesveen &lt;futh...@chromium.org&gt;
wrote:&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

&gt; Four issues are opened against the spec:
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/11181"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/11181&lt;/a&gt;
